metadata.name: Transparent Power #1
metadata.description: The Transparent Powers collection consists of 5000 cards. Owning a Transparent Power card makes you part of a community and give you access to the world of science and gamification. You can be more with Transparent Powers. To access all community perks, you must have at least 1 Transparent Powers NFT. You can find all the details on our Discord channel (in Polish).
